<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA4">
<l>maruntum poruḷu mamutamun tāṉē</l>
<l>tiruntiya ceṅkaṇmā lāṅkē – poruntiya</l>
<l>niṉṟulaka muṇṭumiḻntu nīrēṟṟu mūvaṭiyā</l>
<l>laṉṟulakan tāyō ṉaṭi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Remedy, wealth and ambrosia is he,</l>
<l>Māl with perfect red eyes; there he stood in agreement</l>
<l>[with Bali], having swallowed [and] spit out the world, accepting water,</l>
<l>[and] with three steps of [his] feet he spread over the world that day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
